Abstract: During my Frontend Internship at BlokTrek Technologies Pvt Ltd as 
part of the Practice School 2 (PS2) program at BITS Pilani, I had the 
opportunity to develop a crucial administrative portal with data visualization 
and modification capabilities. Under the guidance of my mentor, Mr. Raam 
Baranidharan, this internship provided hands-on experience in frontend 
development while tackling real-world challenges. This report highlights the 
project's scope, technical implementations, and the invaluable skills acquired, 
demonstrating the practical application of academic knowledge in a 
professional setting . 
 
 
 
                
 
Signature of Student      Signature of PS Faculty  
 
Date: 25th, September, 2023

Introduction 
 
The Practice School 2 (PS2) program at BITS Pilani serves as a cornerstone for 
students to bridge the gap between theoretical knowledge and practical 
application. My tenure as a Frontend Intern at BlokTrek Technologies Pvt Ltd 
during this final semester has been a journey of profound learning and hands-on 
experience. This report aims to elucidate my integral role in the development of 
critical functionalities, specifically focusing on organizational onboarding, user 
creation, and the innovative feature of custom tear sheet creation, catering to the 
dynamic needs of the organization. 
The Evolution of Organizational Onboarding  
In the dynamic realm of business operations, efficient organizational 
onboarding processes are paramount. BlokTrek Technologies entrusted me with 
the task of conceptualizing and implementing a comprehensive system to 
facilitate the seamless integration of new organizations onto their platform. This 
multifaceted system encompassed organization setup, plan assignment, access 
management, and database administration. Leveraging Python, AWS serverless 
architecture, Secrets Manager, and MongoDB, I engineered a robust framework 
that streamlined the onboarding process while upholding stringent security 
measures and scalability. 
Empowering Administrators with User Creation  
In parallel with organizational onboarding, I extended the capabilities of the 
administrative portal to empower administrators with the autonomy to create 
users for organizations. By integrating user creation functionalities seamlessly 
into the existing administrative interface, administrators were equipped with the 
tools to manage user access efficiently, thereby enhancing the overall user 
experience and operational efficiency. 
Innovative Feature: Custom Tear Sheet Creation  
A pivotal addition to the platform was the innovative feature of custom tear 
sheet creation, designed to cater to the diverse needs of users. This feature 
allowed users to create custom question sections, tailor-made to their specific 
requirements, and save them for future use. Upon activation, the system 
dynamically triggered the custom tear sheet creation process, ensuring 
flexibility and responsiveness to user preferences and organizational dynamics.

Mentorship and Growth  
Throughout this transformative journey, I had the privilege of being mentored 
by seasoned professionals at BlokTrek Technologies. Their guidance not only 
enhanced my technical acumen but also provided invaluable insights into the 
nuances of frontend development, database management, and system 
architecture.

Project Description 
 
a) Organizational Onboarding 
Overview  The organizational onboarding system emerged as a pivotal 
component of my role as a Frontend Intern at BlokTrek Technologies Pvt Ltd. 
This system aimed to streamline the integration of new organizations onto the 
platform, encompassing various aspects such as setup, plan assignment, access 
management, and database administration. 
Objectives  
1. Seamless Organization Setup : The primary objective was to design an 
intuitive and efficient process for setting up new organizations on the 
BlokTrek platform. This involved creating interfaces for organization 
profile creation, plan selection, and basic configuration settings. 
2. Dynamic Plan Assignment : The system needed to dynamically assign 
appropriate plans to new organizations based on their requirements and 
preferences. Customization options for plan features and pricing were 
also integrated to accommodate diverse organizational needs. 
3. Granular Access Control : Implementing granular access controls was 
crucial to ensure data security and privacy. The system allowed 
administrators to define role-based access permissions, granting or 
restricting access to specific features and data based on user roles within 
the organization. 
4. Scalable Database Management : A scalable database management 
system was developed to efficiently handle organizational data. Utilizing 
MongoDB for its flexibility and scalability, the system ensured seamless 
data storage, retrieval, and management for each onboarded organization. 
Technologies Utilized  The successful implementation of the organizational 
onboarding system relied on a robust stack of technologies and tools, including: 
 Python: Leveraged for backend logic and server-side scripting to manage 
organizational data and workflows. 
 AWS Serverless Architecture: Utilized to deploy scalable and cost-
effective backend services, ensuring high availability and performance. 
 AWS Secrets Manager: Employed for secure storage and management of 
sensitive credentials and API keys required for accessing external 
services and databases.

 MongoDB: Chosen as the database management system for its flexibility, 
scalability, and support for complex data structures. 
 React: Utilized for frontend development, enabling the creation of 
dynamic and interactive user interfaces for organization setup and 
management.

b) Tear Sheet Generation 
Overview  Another significant feature I worked on during my internship at 
BlokTrek Technologies was the development of a custom tear sheet generation 
functionality. This feature allowed users to create personalized tear sheets 
containing custom questions and sections, tailored to their specific requirements 
and preferences. 
Objectives  
1. Dynamic Question Section Creation : The primary objective was to 
enable users to create custom question sections within tear sheets, 
allowing for flexibility and customization. 
2. User-Friendly Interface : The system aimed to provide an intuitive and 
user-friendly interface for creating and editing tear sheets. Drag-and-drop 
functionality and interactive editing tools were implemented to enhance 
usability. 
3. Data Persistence and Retrieval : It was essential to ensure that user-
created tear sheets were saved persistently and could be retrieved for 
future use. The system implemented robust data storage mechanisms to 
store tear sheet configurations securely. 
4. Automated Triggering : Upon creation or modification of a tear sheet, 
the system dynamically triggered the generation process, ensuring that 
users could access the latest versions of their custom tear sheets 
seamlessly. 
Technologies Utilized  The tear sheet generation feature leveraged a similar 
technology stack to the administrative portal, including: 
 React: Utilized for frontend development, enabling the creation of 
dynamic and responsive user interfaces for tear sheet creation and 
management. 
 JSON Editor: Employed to enhance user interaction and manipulation 
capabilities within the tear sheet editor, enabling users to customize 
question sections and content. 
 Axios: Utilized for efficient data fetching and handling, facilitating 
communication between the frontend and backend systems for tear sheet 
management. 
This comprehensive overview encapsulates the objectives, functionalities, and 
technologies utilized in the development of both the organizational onboarding 
system and tear sheet generation feature during my internship at BlokTrek 
Technologies Pvt Ltd.

Conclusion 
My internship journey at BlokTrek Technologies Pvt Ltd, as part of the Practice 
School 2 (PS2) program at BITS Pilani, has been a transformative odyssey that 
profoundly deepened my comprehension of web development, frontend 
technologies, and their pragmatic utilization in real-world scenarios. 
Throughout this enriching experience, I had the privilege of contributing to the 
evolution of the Administrative Portal and augmenting the functionality of the 
Main Dashboard. 
This internship has yielded several invaluable insights: 
Application of Academic Knowledge: This immersive experience underscored 
the tangible application of theoretical concepts acquired at BITS Pilani. It 
illuminated the seamless transition from classroom theory to real-world project 
execution, effectively bridging the academia-industry divide. 
Frontend Development Proficiency: My journey significantly bolstered my 
competency in frontend development. I acquired proficiency in a spectrum of 
technologies such as React, Material-UI (MUI), Ag-Grid, JSON Editor, and 
Axios, enhancing my marketability in the industry. 
User-Centric Design Philosophy: Emphasizing user-centric design principles 
and elevating the user experience emerged as central tenets of my 
developmental approach. Prioritizing usability and crafting intuitive interfaces 
became recurring themes in my endeavors. 
Problem-Solving and Debugging Acumen: The internship honed my prowess in 
identifying and remedying bugs, optimizing performance, and refining code 
structures for enhanced efficiency. These hands-on experiences fortified my 
problem-solving abilities and debugging proficiency. 
Mentorship and Collaborative Culture: The collaborative ethos at BlokTrek 
Technologies, coupled with the guidance from my mentor, Mr. Raam 
Baranidharan, played a pivotal role in my professional growth. The nurturing 
environment fostered invaluable mentorship and collaborative synergy, 
propelling my developmental trajectory. 
As I culminate this reflective report, I extend heartfelt gratitude to BlokTrek 
Technologies Pvt Ltd and the PS2 program for the enriching opportunities 
bestowed upon me. The knowledge and skills gleaned during this internship not 
only enriched my academic voyage but also equipped me with pragmatic

insights poised to shape my future career trajectory in frontend development 
and beyond. 
I eagerly anticipate applying the lessons imbibed and experiences garnered as I 
navigate through the realms of academia and professional endeavors. This 
internship marks a seminal milestone in my evolution as a frontend developer, 
igniting a fervent passion for software development that resonates deeply within 
me
